      • adjustLineDiscount

        public boolean adjustLineDiscount
        Flag required for default processing for line discounts. This should be returned as true only if the UE implementation has not determined the amount of DISCOUNT charges to be added to the invoice. If the UE is implemented and this boolean flag is not set, it will default to false. If the UE is not implemented this flag will default to true.
